**Women and students of color** **, as defined by N.J.A.C. 17:46-1.2,** **pursuing a**
**certificate or degree in construction-related fields at an eligible county college,**
**vocational school, or proprietary school can receive financial support from the**
**State through NJ-GIVS. This scholarship funded by the New Jersey Schools**
**Development Authority and administered by the New Jersey Higher Education**
**Student Assistance Authority (HESAA) offers up to $2,000 per year for up to**
**two years after all other financial aid has been applied.**



![](/app/user_site/7eb96829-c8f0-4ccc-8e93-53bd92f17441/src/src/assets/givs-images/7bb9a70e30bc4f0e854f0f68c1b2efa2.pdf-0-3.png)

